msgid "GPS定位获取到的数据如何转换？（针对A9G、EC-01G以及GP-01/GP-02模组）"
msgstr "How to convert the GPS positioning data? (For A9G, EC-01G, and GP-01/GP-02 modules)"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/NB/index.rst:16 e41df2641dc04c2a9de4b5694fa68bb9
msgid "答：获取到GNGGA经纬度数据需转换公式：data/100 + data(整数部分)%100/60 + data(小数部分)/600000。 获取到的数据为WGS84坐标系，还需转换为GCJ02坐标系。"
msgstr ""
"A: The obtained GNGGA latitude and longitude data needs to be converted using the following formula: data/100 + integer part of data %100/60 + decimal part of data/600000.\n"
"The obtained data is in the WGS84 coordinate system and also needs to be converted to the GCJ02 coordinate system."

