msgid "NB-IoT是窄宽带的应用，用于传输小数据量的应用；而2G/3G/4G/5G移动网络用于大数据量的传输，如文件传输，视频下载等等；"
msgstr "NB-IoT is a narrowband application used for transmitting small amounts of data; while 2G/3G/4G/5G mobile networks are used for large data transmission, such as file transfer, video download, etc."

